I actually need something.

355
00:26:11,421 --> 00:26:12,422
What is it now?

356
00:26:12,589 --> 00:26:16,927
We need original music for the
Street Food Challenge content.

357
00:26:18,410 --> 00:26:19,661
Original music?

358
00:26:20,617 --> 00:26:21,617
Why me?

359
00:26:21,642 --> 00:26:23,310
Your company is huge.

360
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:24,920
Why not get someone from there?

361
00:26:24,944 --> 00:26:26,085
Well, of course.

362
00:26:26,404 --> 00:26:29,421
You’re the best
songwriter I know.

363
00:26:31,117 --> 00:26:32,257
Now you’re just flattering me.

364
00:26:32,786 --> 00:26:33,884
But come on, agree already.

365
00:26:34,287 --> 00:26:35,979
Come on, say yes.
I saw you smile.

366
00:26:36,003 --> 00:26:38,047
Best songwriter
in the Philippines.

367
00:26:38,798 --> 00:26:39,799
You know that,

368
00:26:40,633 --> 00:26:42,319
I’ll go anywhere with you.

369
00:26:42,343 --> 00:26:43,427
As long as I don’t have a gig.

370
00:26:44,011 --> 00:26:46,764
So include me in your team.

371
00:26:48,266 --> 00:26:49,559
You’re the best, ugly.

372
00:26:49,559 --> 00:26:52,746
You know what,
I’ll tell Helga that I’ll handle the music.

373
00:26:52,770 --> 00:26:57,024
And I’ll also tell her that you’re
part of my team so you can come.

374
00:26:57,024 --> 00:26:58,024
Okay?

375
00:26:58,651 --> 00:27:00,153
I'm so excited.

376
00:27:00,153 --> 00:27:01,153
Wait, wait, wait.

377
00:27:02,655 --> 00:27:04,907
But you already have a
lot of music saved up, right?

378
00:27:05,408 --> 00:27:06,534
Yes, a lot.

379
00:27:07,076 --> 00:27:09,078
I knew it,
you’re perfect for this.

380
00:27:11,372 --> 00:27:12,372
Okay.

381
00:27:12,725 --> 00:27:14,227
Okay, this works.

382
00:27:57,534 --> 00:27:59,260
Sir, it's not ready yet.

383
00:27:59,261 --> 00:28:00,888
I still can't show this to you.

384
00:28:06,476 --> 00:28:08,061
Alright, one pose.

385
00:28:08,061 --> 00:28:09,146
Next, please.

386
00:28:09,897 --> 00:28:11,190
Last one for me.

387
00:28:12,107 --> 00:28:13,775
Alright, very good, Chanwoo.

388
00:28:16,125 --> 00:28:18,502
For the next setup,
we need a 30-minute break.

389
00:28:18,502 --> 00:28:20,671
So, let's be back
at 3 p.m. Okay?

390
00:28:21,224 --> 00:28:22,224
Thank you.

391
00:28:23,124 --> 00:28:24,327
Thank you.

392
00:28:24,870 --> 00:28:25,954
Thank you, Melody.

393
00:28:41,412 --> 00:28:42,596
- Ugly.
- What?

394
00:28:42,605 --> 00:28:45,849
I thought we were just
changing the setup? Why...

395
00:28:46,592 --> 00:28:47,935
did everyone disappear?

396
00:28:47,938 --> 00:28:49,996
Ah, they’re just hungry.

397
00:28:50,020 --> 00:28:51,063
They’ll be back right away.

398
00:28:51,087 --> 00:28:52,648
It’s a 30-minute break anyway.

399
00:28:53,016 --> 00:28:54,143
30 minutes?

400
00:28:55,329 --> 00:28:56,622
Then let’s eat first.

401
00:28:57,722 --> 00:28:59,878
I saw something over there,
it looks good.

402
00:28:59,902 --> 00:29:01,865
I still need to send something.

403
00:29:01,890 --> 00:29:04,393
- Wait, I’ll just get something first.
- What are you getting?

404
00:29:04,543 --> 00:29:05,689
I’ll handle it,

405
00:29:05,713 --> 00:29:07,380
so you can finish
what you’re doing.

406
00:29:07,546 --> 00:29:09,507
- Are you sure?
- Yes, what is it?

407
00:29:09,507 --> 00:29:11,759
The hard drive,
my bag is in the van.

408
00:29:11,759 --> 00:29:13,019
- Hard drive?
- Yes, go get it,

409
00:29:13,043 --> 00:29:15,587
the photographer might look
for one of the looks here later.

410
00:29:15,611 --> 00:29:16,688
- Okay.
- Go get it,

411
00:29:16,712 --> 00:29:18,401
- I’ll fix things here. Hurry up.
- Okay.

412
00:29:20,394 --> 00:29:21,520
Is this right?

413
00:29:25,412 --> 00:29:27,581
Ah, one is missing.

414
00:29:32,012 --> 00:29:33,012
Melody.

415
00:29:34,348 --> 00:29:35,933
Can I talk to you privately?

416
00:29:39,708 --> 00:29:42,908
Uh, we are,
we are already talking.

417
00:29:44,208 --> 00:29:45,626
Do we have a problem?

418
00:29:46,435 --> 00:29:47,435
Problem?

419
00:29:47,441 --> 00:29:48,965
What problem?

420
00:29:50,688 --> 00:29:51,688
I can't help

421
00:29:52,635 --> 00:29:54,262
but feel like something's wrong.

422
00:29:56,018 --> 00:29:57,144
Or maybe

423
00:29:57,587 --> 00:29:59,673
I did something to upset you.

424
00:30:01,812 --> 00:30:03,272
You've been acting a bit cold.

425
00:30:04,898 --> 00:30:08,443
And since I really
value our team's energy,

426
