I just wanted to check in.

427
00:30:14,176 --> 00:30:15,552
Did I do something wrong?

428
00:30:17,380 --> 00:30:18,840
I'm not cold sir.

429
00:30:21,092 --> 00:30:22,092
I don't know.

430
00:30:23,427 --> 00:30:28,057
I just feel like you're
always on guard around me.

431
00:30:29,672 --> 00:30:31,090
Is there a reason for that?

432
00:30:33,217 --> 00:30:34,217
Where's...

433
00:30:41,713 --> 00:30:43,841
This was from three years ago.

434
00:30:45,134 --> 00:30:47,930
Actually, four.

435
00:30:49,266 --> 00:30:50,266
I see.

436
00:30:51,026 --> 00:30:52,026
You're a fan.

437
00:30:54,728 --> 00:30:56,021
Please don't tell Helga.

438
00:30:56,396 --> 00:30:57,396
Don't worry.

439
00:30:57,981 --> 00:30:58,981
I won't tell her.

440
00:30:59,574 --> 00:31:00,826
I actually thought

441
00:31:01,576 --> 00:31:03,737
you couldn't stand
being around me.

442
00:31:05,205 --> 00:31:09,459
So, I'm glad to find
out I was wrong.

443
