I'm sorry.

444
00:31:12,234 --> 00:31:13,234
Don't be sorry.

445
00:31:13,789 --> 00:31:14,831
It's good to know.

446
00:31:35,599 --> 00:31:36,839
This is kwek-kwek.

447
00:31:37,312 --> 00:31:39,665
It's a quail egg
with orange batter.

448
00:31:39,689 --> 00:31:41,441
This one, it's isaw.

449
00:31:42,275 --> 00:31:44,361
It's chicken intestines.

450
00:31:44,361 --> 00:31:45,892
You know what?
You should try that.

451
00:31:45,916 --> 00:31:47,792
It's really delicious.
I promise.

452
00:31:49,084 --> 00:31:50,667
- Isaw?
- Yeah, it's clean.

453
00:31:50,668 --> 00:31:51,668
Okay.

454
00:31:52,813 --> 00:31:53,813
Is it good?

455
00:31:53,838 --> 00:31:55,398
- Try it.
- Okay.

456
00:31:55,423 --> 00:31:56,800
I trust you, Melody.

457
00:31:57,884 --> 00:31:59,469
You have very good taste.

458
00:31:59,469 --> 00:32:01,947
And since you're a longtime fan,

459
00:32:01,971 --> 00:32:05,225
I assume you know
personal things about me.

460
00:32:11,398 --> 00:32:13,166
Oh. Hey there, ugly.

461
00:32:13,191 --> 00:32:14,348
Come here. Come here.

462
00:32:14,355 --> 00:32:16,382
Come here.
I’ll introduce you to my friend.

463
00:32:17,060 --> 00:32:18,060
Yeah.

464
00:32:18,478 --> 00:32:19,478
Get the chair.

465
00:32:20,522 --> 00:32:21,940
This is George.

466
00:32:22,273 --> 00:32:24,109
He's the songwriter
I told you about.

467
00:32:24,109 --> 00:32:26,194
He's also the one in
charge of the music

468
00:32:26,206 --> 00:32:28,792
for the Street Food
Challenge content.

469
00:32:29,510 --> 00:32:30,510
Nice to meet you, George.

470
00:32:31,762 --> 00:32:32,762
I'm George.

471
00:32:34,303 --> 00:32:36,496
You must be very, very good.

472
00:32:37,703 --> 00:32:40,834
I respect songwriters
like you very much.

473
00:32:41,082 --> 00:32:44,338
Your work makes mine feel real.

474
00:32:44,826 --> 00:32:49,760
The truth is I want to
write my own songs, too.

475
00:32:51,541 --> 00:32:52,792
Can you give me pointers?

476
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:57,225
No. No,
I'm just a small songwriter.

477
00:32:57,589 --> 00:32:59,256
Oh, no. He sings, too.

478
