I think every Filipino can sing.

479
00:33:03,354 --> 00:33:08,001
Now, I am getting nervous
for my upcoming concert.

480
00:33:08,025 --> 00:33:09,110
No, Chanwoo.

481
00:33:09,402 --> 00:33:11,487
Yours is very different.

482
00:33:11,737 --> 00:33:14,699
We Filipinos,
we just sing in karaoke.

483
00:33:14,699 --> 00:33:18,035
But your voice is the best,
I promise.

484
00:33:18,578 --> 00:33:20,180
You always say that.

485
00:33:20,204 --> 00:33:21,998
Because you're my fan.

486
00:33:22,665 --> 00:33:24,584
Don't let Helga hear that, okay?

487
00:33:27,086 --> 00:33:29,964
My concert is next week.

488
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:32,091
I hope you'll enjoy.

489
00:33:33,843 --> 00:33:38,490
Actually, you're so famous here that
my friend and I failed to get your tickets.

490
00:33:38,514 --> 00:33:39,616
It was sold out.

491
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,475
- Really?
- Yeah.

492
00:33:43,478 --> 00:33:44,478
I'm sorry.

493
00:33:45,146 --> 00:33:46,146
You missed out.

494
00:33:47,648 --> 00:33:51,444
Look, if you can't get
into the main show.

495
00:33:51,444 --> 00:33:57,450
I'm doing a few pocket performances
and press conferences around town.

496
00:33:59,410 --> 00:34:01,162
I'd love for you to come.

497
00:34:02,580 --> 00:34:03,580
Bring your friend.

498
00:34:04,081 --> 00:34:05,081
George can come too.

499
00:34:08,127 --> 00:34:11,172
My assistant will
send over the details.

500
00:34:11,714 --> 00:34:12,882
Oh my gosh, oh my
gosh, oh my gosh.

501
00:34:13,341 --> 00:34:15,593
Pangit! Thank you,
thank you, thank you.

502
00:34:16,594 --> 00:34:18,947
But before that,
I think we have to go back.

503
00:34:18,971 --> 00:34:19,971
With our content.

504
00:34:20,649 --> 00:34:22,685
Okay, so what's this again?
Do you remember?

505
00:34:22,709 --> 00:34:23,709
This?

506
00:34:24,752 --> 00:34:26,378
- This what?
- The quail egg?

507
00:34:26,403 --> 00:34:27,403
What do you call this?

508
00:34:28,607 --> 00:34:29,607
It's kwek-kwek.

509
00:34:29,632 --> 00:34:30,632
Kwek-kwek.

