into lying that you’re not here.

777
00:55:08,296 --> 00:55:09,923
You won’t even reply to me, huh?

778
00:55:10,882 --> 00:55:12,675
You just keep uploading songs.

779
00:55:13,301 --> 00:55:14,301
Why?

780
00:55:15,503 --> 00:55:18,423
I know nothing's going to happen
even if I upload that song.

781
00:55:19,497 --> 00:55:20,664
Aren’t you happy now?

782
00:55:21,415 --> 00:55:22,583
Happy about what?

783
00:55:24,126 --> 00:55:25,127
George,

784
00:55:26,545 --> 00:55:29,799
you suddenly confess your feelings
to everyone else and then,

785
00:55:30,341 --> 00:55:31,592
but not to me?

786
00:55:32,593 --> 00:55:33,928
Why didn’t you tell me?

787
00:55:35,221 --> 00:55:39,433
Your song about me became so famous,
and I’m the last to know?

788
00:55:40,100 --> 00:55:41,894
Would anything
change if I told you?

789
00:55:45,149 --> 00:55:48,485
Are you here because
the song got popular?

790
00:55:54,229 --> 00:55:55,814
Is that how you see me?

791
00:55:58,509 --> 00:56:02,805
George, I already resigned
from the company.

792
00:56:04,431 --> 00:56:06,225
I also said goodbye to Chanwoo.

793
00:56:16,026 --> 00:56:17,278
Just answer me honestly, Mel.

794
00:56:18,779 --> 00:56:20,906
Aren’t you crazy in love
with your Chanwoo?

795
00:56:22,116 --> 00:56:23,116
And then what?

796
00:56:24,285 --> 00:56:25,285
You’re here now?

797
00:56:26,704 --> 00:56:27,830
What’s going to happen?

798
00:56:29,290 --> 00:56:31,333
Do you even know what
you want to happen?

799
00:56:38,591 --> 00:56:39,591
I'm sorry, George.

800
00:56:43,762 --> 00:56:46,390
You know what,
let’s take a break first.

801
00:56:49,226 --> 00:56:52,521
Feel things out first and
figure out what’s real for you.

802
00:56:53,564 --> 00:56:54,940
I’ll figure out if...

803
00:56:56,025 --> 00:56:57,276
I still love you.

804
00:57:46,033 --> 00:57:47,493
I’ll play at the soundcheck.

805
00:57:48,243 --> 00:57:49,703
There might be a
lot of people there.

806
00:58:17,022 --> 00:58:18,273
Coffee latte for Melody.

807
00:58:18,607 --> 00:58:19,942
Thank you.

808
00:58:46,427 --> 00:58:48,113
Miss, can I share?

809
00:58:48,137 --> 00:58:49,137
Oh, it’s—

810
00:58:53,058 --> 00:58:54,058
George.

811
00:58:55,102 --> 00:58:56,395
I thought you were busy?

812
00:58:57,229 --> 00:58:58,313
I heard

813
00:58:58,939 --> 00:59:00,190
you’re going on a world tour.

814
00:59:01,191 --> 00:59:04,004
Hey, you searched
my name, didn’t you?

815
00:59:04,028 --> 00:59:05,255
That’s touching.

816
00:59:05,279 --> 00:59:07,656
Even if I didn’t search,
you’re already famous.

817
00:59:08,323 --> 00:59:10,951
I hear and see you everywhere.

818
00:59:14,371 --> 00:59:15,456
You know, Mel,

819
00:59:16,331 --> 00:59:18,584
it’s always been my dream
to be known by everyone.

820
00:59:18,876 --> 00:59:19,876
Right?

821
00:59:20,919 --> 00:59:22,129
But honestly,

822
00:59:23,630 --> 00:59:26,175
there’s only one
person I want to please.

823
00:59:31,430 --> 00:59:35,267
Up until now, you still don’t
know how to say things directly?

824
00:59:38,228 --> 00:59:39,372
I’m sorry.

825
00:59:39,396 --> 00:59:40,396
Here.

826
00:59:41,565 --> 00:59:42,565
Okay.

827
00:59:53,869 --> 00:59:55,579
My song has a new ending now.

828
00:59:57,206 --> 01:00:00,417
And in this version,
I won’t let go.

829
01:00:02,169 --> 01:00:03,796
I won’t hesitate anymore.

830
01:00:05,522 --> 01:00:06,940
And I won’t be afraid.

831
01:00:09,927 --> 01:00:10,927
Of what?

832
01:00:18,811 --> 01:00:20,354
Of saying it’s only you.

833
01:00:23,440 --> 01:00:24,440
That it’s still you.

834
01:00:26,902 --> 01:00:28,320
That I still love you.

835
01:00:30,697 --> 01:00:32,282
And no matter what
your answer is, Mel,

836
01:00:33,784 --> 01:00:35,285
that will never change.

837
01:01:02,771 --> 01:01:05,774
Love doesn’t need to be loud.

838
01:01:06,275 --> 01:01:11,238
The real measure is when,
even in silence, you're happy.

839
01:01:11,822 --> 01:01:18,606
Not what you want,
but who you can’t bear to lose.
